# Complete Frontend dApp Implementation Plan

The objective is to build the entire production-grade Next.js frontend for the MST Supply Chain dApp. The frontend will integrate seamlessly with the existing NestJS backend and smart contracts using real-time, non-mock data. We will enforce strict atomic code generation, zero mock drift, and immediate verification hooks (linting/compiling after every step).

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> During my audit of the existing backend, I discovered that the `POST /api/checkpoint` endpoint (mentioned in the presentation script for Phase 4) **does not exist** in the backend code. 
> To achieve "Zero Mock Drift", I must first implement this missing backend module (`checkpoint.controller.ts` & `checkpoint.service.ts`) before building the frontend transporter UI.

